cs.DB, cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with the study of influence of ordinal transformations on results of queries in rank-aware databases, which is a topic related to databases and logic. Therefore, cs.DB and cs.LO are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also introduces notions of ordinal containment and equivalence of ranked relations, which are related to artificial intelligence and machine learning, hence cs.AI is also a likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the relationship to monotone query evaluation and alternative rank-aware approaches, which are related to data structures and algorithms, hence cs.DS and cs.LG are also likely sub-categories.
